{
  "id": "5fe79bb4acfc01001e2507c6",
  "title": "自炊本をScrapboxに変換する手順",
  "created": 1609014200,
  "updated": 1661162454,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "5fe79bb4acfc01001e2507c6",
      "text": "自炊本をScrapboxに変換する手順",
      "userId": "566fa156776c9b11008ee92a",
      "created": 1609014200,
      "updated": 1609014200
    },
    {
      "id": "5fe79c0c8ee92a000043eeb6",
      "text": "[増井俊之.icon] の方法",
      "userId": "566fa156776c9b11008ee92a",
      "created": 1609014285,
      "updated": 1609014297
    },
    {
      "id": "5fe79bb78ee92a000043eeaf",
      "text": " [本]を裁断する",
      "userId": "566fa156776c9b11008ee92a",
      "created": 1609014200,
      "updated": 1609014314
    },
    {
      "id": "5fe79c2a8ee92a000043eeb7",
      "text": " [ScanSnap]でスキャンして[PDF]化する",
      "userId": "566fa156776c9b11008ee92a",
      "created": 1609014314,
      "updated": 1609014828
    },
    {
      "id": "5fe79bc18ee92a000043eeb1",
      "text": " ページごとに画像に変換する",
      "userId": "566fa156776c9b11008ee92a",
      "created": 1609014210,
      "updated": 1609014220
    },
    {
      "id": "607a080d8ee92a0000a0335d",
      "text": "  [pdfimages]というコマンドが使える",
      "userId": "566fa156776c9b11008ee92a",
      "created": 1618610189,
      "updated": 1618610204
    },
    {
      "id": "5fe79bce8ee92a000043eeb2",
      "text": " 全ページをGyazoにアップロード",
      "userId": "566fa156776c9b11008ee92a",
      "created": 1609014222,
      "updated": 1609014233
    },
    {
      "id": "5fe79bda8ee92a000043eeb3",
      "text": " (Gyazoにアップロードしたものは自動的にOCRされる)",
      "userId": "566fa156776c9b11008ee92a",
      "created": 1609014234,
      "updated": 1609014540
    },
    {
      "id": "5fe79bec8ee92a000043eeb4",
      "text": " (OCRが完了するのを待つ)",
      "userId": "566fa156776c9b11008ee92a",
      "created": 1609014252,
      "updated": 1609014265
    },
    {
      "id": "5fe79bfa8ee92a000043eeb5",
      "text": " ページの画像とOCR結果テキストをまとめてJSONにする",
      "userId": "566fa156776c9b11008ee92a",
      "created": 1609014266,
      "updated": 1609014361
    },
    {
      "id": "5fe79c5a8ee92a000043eeb8",
      "text": " Scrapboxで読み込む",
      "userId": "566fa156776c9b11008ee92a",
      "created": 1609014362,
      "updated": 1609014371
    },
    {
      "id": "5fe84d3ee5172d00008217b6",
      "text": " \t全文が入ったすごくでかいページができるんだろうか、それとも適当なところでページを分けるんだろうか[yosider.icon]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1609059648,
      "updated": 1609059713
    },
    {
      "id": "5fe853418ee92a00000c3a17",
      "text": " \t書籍の1ページごとにScrapboxのページを作ってます [増井俊之.icon]",
      "userId": "566fa156776c9b11008ee92a",
      "created": 1609061186,
      "updated": 1609061203
    },
    {
      "id": "5fe853848ee92a00000c3a19",
      "text": " \t 200ページの本なら200ページのScrapboxプロジェクトができる",
      "userId": "566fa156776c9b11008ee92a",
      "created": 1609061253,
      "updated": 1609061264
    },
    {
      "id": "5fe853528ee92a00000c3a18",
      "text": " \t 全文1ページに入れてる猛者がいるらしいけど重いからやめてほしい",
      "userId": "566fa156776c9b11008ee92a",
      "created": 1609061203,
      "updated": 1609061220
    },
    {
      "id": "5fe85793e5172d0000a7d6e8",
      "text": " \t [/icons/なるほど.icon]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1609062293,
      "updated": 1609062335
    },
    {
      "id": "5fe857d6e5172d0000a7d6e9",
      "text": " \t ページが文の中途半端なところで切れてしまうのは、まあ仕方ないのかな",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1609062360,
      "updated": 1609062417
    },
    {
      "id": "5fe8984c8ee92a0000ef6716",
      "text": " \t それは[Kindle]でも同じですよね [増井俊之.icon]",
      "userId": "566fa156776c9b11008ee92a",
      "created": 1609078861,
      "updated": 1609078876
    },
    {
      "id": "5fe899cce5172d0000861858",
      "text": " \t \t次のページにすぐ遷移できるなら別によさそう",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1609079243,
      "updated": 1609079261
    },
    {
      "id": "5fe8a1358ee92a0000ef672c",
      "text": " \t \t矢印キーで遷移できるUserScriptを使ってます [増井俊之.icon]",
      "userId": "566fa156776c9b11008ee92a",
      "created": 1609081142,
      "updated": 1609081160
    },
    {
      "id": "5fe8b783e5172d00001c6045",
      "text": " \t \t\t[/icons/よさそう.icon]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1609086852,
      "updated": 1609086853
    },
    {
      "id": "5fe79bb88ee92a000043eeb0",
      "text": " サンプル",
      "userId": "566fa156776c9b11008ee92a",
      "created": 1609014200,
      "updated": 1609014462
    },
    {
      "id": "5fe79d2e8ee92a000043eebd",
      "text": "  [/masuibook-fukuzatsusa]",
      "userId": "566fa156776c9b11008ee92a",
      "created": 1609014575,
      "updated": 1609014576
    },
    {
      "id": "5fe79eab8ee92a000043eeca",
      "text": "  [https://gyazo.com/67e90bae5e5843dc1faa92e1e68aeaa8]",
      "userId": "566fa156776c9b11008ee92a",
      "created": 1609014956,
      "updated": 1609014956
    },
    {
      "id": "5fe79cb18ee92a000043eeb9",
      "text": "  [https://gyazo.com/93f05075d43bb77191b228078be8daf2]",
      "userId": "566fa156776c9b11008ee92a",
      "created": 1609014449,
      "updated": 1609014463
    },
    {
      "id": "5fe79cb38ee92a000043eebb",
      "text": "  [https://gyazo.com/17b0d2538fbe837748f8845e377ff476]",
      "userId": "566fa156776c9b11008ee92a",
      "created": 1609014451,
      "updated": 1609014495
    },
    {
      "id": "5fe79cdf8ee92a000043eebc",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "566fa156776c9b11008ee92a",
      "created": 1609014495,
      "updated": 1609014495
    },
    {
      "id": "5fe79d738ee92a000043eebe",
      "text": " 裁断とかスキャンとかデータ変換とか面倒臭いけど、どこでも読めるようになるし[全文検索]できるのはとても嬉しい",
      "userId": "566fa156776c9b11008ee92a",
      "created": 1609014644,
      "updated": 1609014977
    },
    {
      "id": "600b783379d3a900008e864d",
      "text": "\t\t作業時間どれくらいです？200pageの本で数時間くらいかかりそうなイメージがある",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1611364394,
      "updated": 1611364395
    },
    {
      "id": "600b8ad88ee92a000056e396",
      "text": "\t\tほとんど自動なのでそこまでかからないですね [増井俊之.icon]",
      "userId": "566fa156776c9b11008ee92a",
      "created": 1611369176,
      "updated": 1611369197
    },
    {
      "id": "600b8b1f8ee92a000056e397",
      "text": "\t\t 20-30分ぐらい?",
      "userId": "566fa156776c9b11008ee92a",
      "created": 1611369247,
      "updated": 1611369255
    },
    {
      "id": "600b8b3d8ee92a000056e398",
      "text": "\t\t 裁断は練習次第だけど1分はかからない気がする",
      "userId": "566fa156776c9b11008ee92a",
      "created": 1611369277,
      "updated": 1611369323
    },
    {
      "id": "6014fdf079d3a9000079a3e2",
      "text": "\t\t ありがとうございます。普通に現実的ですね[sta.icon]",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1611988456,
      "updated": 1611988467
    },
    {
      "id": "5fe79e4f8ee92a000043eec7",
      "text": " 自炊したPDFがあればコマンド一発でScrapbox用のJSONを生成できる",
      "userId": "566fa156776c9b11008ee92a",
      "created": 1609014863,
      "updated": 1609014892
    },
    {
      "id": "5fe79d758ee92a000043eebf",
      "text": " Gyazoの[IvySearch]で関連書籍の画像が出てくるのは面白い",
      "userId": "566fa156776c9b11008ee92a",
      "created": 1609014645,
      "updated": 1609014722
    },
    {
      "id": "600a98b379d3a900007a2b8c",
      "text": "　[/icons/よさそう.icon][mtane0412.icon]",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1611307180,
      "updated": 1618146309
    },
    {
      "id": "630343d3b8bbfc0000c0ea78",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1661158356,
      "updated": 1661158356
    },
    {
      "id": "630343d3b8bbfc0000c0ea7a",
      "text": "[アクティブ読書]に使う",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1661158356,
      "updated": 1661158370
    },
    {
      "id": "6072f3fc55cbd30000ecac41",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1618146300,
      "updated": 1618146300
    },
    {
      "id": "63035376a9108b0000b7b0d1",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5fb29108ce01660038a9108b",
      "created": 1661162358,
      "updated": 1661162358
    },
    {
      "id": "63035376a9108b0000b7b0d2",
      "text": "[Kindle]版で買ってる場合はPDFに変換する部分の壁が高い...[amemy.icon]",
      "userId": "5fb29108ce01660038a9108b",
      "created": 1661162358,
